            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-copy-1609936289077-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After the onions have been slowly caramelising for 15 min, add 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp] </span><strong>brown sugar</strong> and a splash of <strong>cold water</strong> and cook for a further 3-4 min</p><p>Then remove from the heat and set aside</p><p>Slice the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong> into 4 <span class=\"text-danger\">[8]</span> slices</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
